27:50.636 --> 27:54.304
16-foot slab with this
sled, and it works perfectly.

27:54.340 --> 27:56.473
If I get about
three more dogs,

27:56.509 --> 27:58.909
I could probably just
load the entire sled up.

27:58.944 --> 28:01.111
But for right now, we need
these dogs to get in shape

28:01.147 --> 28:03.847
before I really start puttin'
the miles and weight on 'em.

28:03.883 --> 28:06.450
But this is just
early season training,

28:06.485 --> 28:09.586
and they're already
getting work done.

28:12.224 --> 28:14.024
Whoa!

28:14.060 --> 28:16.260
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

28:16.295 --> 28:18.062
Whoa!

28:18.097 --> 28:19.997
Good dogs.

