And so, what you're seeing
here is a traditional way to

28:27.640 --> 28:29.039
move stuff around.

28:29.075 --> 28:31.542
Goods and supplies,
freight, lumber, firewood.

28:31.577 --> 28:33.010
You name it.

28:33.045 --> 28:36.480
All you gotta do is just
fire up a few malamutes.

28:38.317 --> 28:40.851
All right.
Time to go with another team.

